WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.500
Start on the exact operational screen for this guide.

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:05.000
Revenue is for business decisions; Payments is for reconciliation.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.500
Set the date range before reading any number.

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:10.000
Read total revenue, current month, average booking value, and average rental length together.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.500
Use charts for signal and detailed rows for context before changing pricing or fleet decisions.

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:15.000
Do not make pricing or fleet changes from one number without checking context and time period.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.500
Use revenue screens to turn performance signals into pricing or fleet decisions.
